name: Wounded Wookiee
Lore: 'When blaster fire from the barge''s gun hit Chewie''s skiff, his leg was injured by shrapnel. This setback distracted the Rebels, causing them to momentarily lose their advantage.',
Text: 'During a battle, if opponent drew more than two battle destiny, cancel all but two of those destiny draws (your choice). OR If your nonunique alien is in a battle, cancel game text of one Rebel present for remainder of turn. OR Cancel Clash Of Sabers.',
